      <div class="container grid-2">
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2 class="reveal">About Picasso Academy</h2>
          <p>Picasso Academy specializes in teaching Spanish as a foreign language, preparing students for academic life in Spain, and offering cultural immersion through language camps. We prioritize communicative proficiency, cultural competence and university-level preparation.</p>
          <p><strong>Mission:</strong> Empower Moroccan students through high-quality Spanish education and trusted administrative support to pursue studies in Spain.</p>
          <p><strong>Vision:</strong> Be the leading bridge between Moroccan learners and Spanish academic opportunities, combining excellence in teaching with cultural experiences.</p>
          <p><strong>Director:</strong> Mohamed Reda Nafihi — over 20 years’ experience in language training, exam preparation and student counselling for study abroad.</p>
          <div class="team-photos">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524504388940-b1c1722653e1?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Team" loading="lazy">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524758631624-e2822e304c36?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Classroom" loading="lazy">
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="about-stats">
          <div class="card reveal">
            <h3>95%+</h3>
            <p>Exam success rate (DELE / SIELE)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card reveal">
            <h3>20+</h3>
            <p>Years of combined teaching experience</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card reveal">
            <h3>Official</h3>
